Isiganwa

Umunsi umwe, urukwavu rwabonye Ikinyamujonjorerwa rubwira Ikinyamujonjorerwa ruti: "Ntushobora kwiruka! Icyo uzi n'ukunyerera hasi."

Ikinyamujonjorerwa kiti: "Uzaze ku cyumweru uzabona."

Ikinyamujonjorerwa cyateguye ibice ijana byimpapuro kandi byanditseho ubutumwa bumwe.

Ikinyamujonjorerwa cyahaye inshuti zacyo impapuro zanditseho ngo : "Urukwavu ni ruza hano umpamagara, umwe muri mwe agomba kuvuga ati: Ndi Ikinyamujonjorerwa."

Ikinyamujonjorerwa kisaba inshuti zacyo kwihisha inyuma y'ibihuru aho urukwavu n'ikinyamujonjorerwa bigomba kunyura.

Ku cyumweru, urukwavu rwahageze rusanga Ikinyamujonjorerwa cyahageze. Urukwavu raravuze ruti: "Reka dutagire irushanwa. Ariko ndatsinda."

Ibinyamushongo byari ku murongo wo gusiganwa ku buryo igihe cyose urukwavu rwanyuze, igisimba cyasakuzaga kiti: 'Ndi igisimba ...' Mu gihe cyo gusiganwa, urukwavu rwahamagaye ruti: "Igisimba! Igisimba!"

Imwe mu njangwe yari yihishe inyuma y'ibihuru yarashubije iti: "Ndi Ikinyamujonjorerwa, ndi Ikinyamujonjorerwa."

Kumusozo w'irushanwa, urukwavu rwarushye cyane. Ruryama hasi, ruti: "Ikinyamujonjorerwa, ndarushye cyane; uratsinze."

Ikinyamujonjorerwa  cyaratsinze kubera ubuhanga bwacyo!
